        run, you can enter an interval, given as a number of days, here. If
        you  run  Announcer each day of the week, and have the interval set
        to  7,  a  message  will  only be posted once a week anyway. If you
        don't give an interval, or an interval of zero, the message will be
        posted each time the program is run.
        
        You may also tell Announcer only to post messages on certain dates,
        then  prefix  the  date with an at sign ("@"). Please note that you
        actually need to run Announcer on that date, if you don't, it won't
